                 rdfs:domain :Incident ;
                 rdfs:range :IncidentType ;
                 rdfs:comment "Relates an incident to its type, modelled as a controlled classification." ;
                 rdfs:label "has incident type" .


###  https://zatopek73.github.io/PAC2_Ontology#hasManufacturedBy
:hasManufacturedBy rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                   rdfs:domain :Device ;
                   rdfs:range :Manufacturer ;
                   rdfs:comment "Relates a device to its manufacturer. Each device is associated with exactly one manufacturer." ;
                   rdfs:label "has manufactured by" .


